WEBVTT

00:01.780 --> 00:05.491
Grace Roberts lives 300 kilometers from the nearest town.

00:06.509 --> 00:08.179
She's never seen an ice cream truck.

00:09.938 --> 00:11.166
Josh Millard lives in Adelaide,...

00:11.590 --> 00:15.161
...loves his soccer, but he's never been to an international game.

00:17.171 --> 00:21.785
Robert Turnbull is 62 years old, and he's never been to the ocean.

00:24.568 --> 00:28.643
All three of them are about to experience these things for the first time.

00:56.017 --> 00:58.957
The new Sony 4K Ultra HDTV.

00:59.597 --> 01:03.795
Detail, color, sound like nothing you've ever experienced.

